    title: `Study MRes and MPhil in the UK: Conditions, Dependent Visas, and Courses`,
    date: "2025-05-12",
    author: `Universitio Team`,
    excerpt: `Dreaming of studying at top UK universities? MRes and MPhil degrees, focused on research, offer a gateway to academic and professional success. Offered at institutions like Oxford and UCL, these progr...`,
    image: "blog-images/united-kingdom-1.webp",
