    title: `Your Complete Guide to Studying Foundation Year in the UK`,
    date: "2025-05-12",
    author: `Universitio Team`,
    excerpt: `Ready to unlock a UK university degree? Studying a Foundation Year in the UK bridges the gap for international students (ages 16–18) transitioning from GCSEs or equivalent to undergraduate studies. Wi...`,
